  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research aims to provide a better understanding of the factors associated with the
      evolution of behavioral addictions, and compliance with care. The investigators thus aim to
      follow patients with several types of behavioral addictions, based on addictive,
      sociodemographic, clinical and endophenotypical characteristics, as well as their care
      adhesion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
