    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria :

        - All consecutive patients seeking treatment at the University Hospital of Nantes for a
        behavioral addiction and age over 15 will be allowed to participate to the study.

        Exclusion Criteria :

          -  Cognitive impairment incompatible with the assessment

          -  Difficulty for writing or reading the French language, incompatible with the
             assessement

          -  Gardianship
      </textblock>
